---
import GeneralLayout from "../layouts/GeneralLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<GeneralLayout title="Beto Montoya | Pro Padel Player">
  <section
    id="inicio"
    class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-primary overflow-hidden"
  >
    <img
      src="../../src/assets/main-hero.webp"
      alt="Fondo decorativo Beto Montoya"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-top object-cover opacity-30"
    />

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4">
      <h2
        class="text-secondary font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        Jugador Profesional de Pádel
      </h2>
      <h1
        class="text-white text-6xl md:text-9xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.85] mb-6"
      >
        Beto <br />
        Montoya
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-lg font-light italic">
        "Dominando la pista con precisión, potencia y la elegancia del juego
        estratégico."
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
      <div
        class="w-[2px] h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-transparent rounded-full"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-black py-16 border-y border-white/10">
    <div
      class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center"
    >
      <div class="group">
        <p
          class="text-secondary text-5xl font-black mb-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          #876
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-400 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] font-bold"
        >
          Ranking Global
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group border-y md:border-y-0 md:border-x border-white/10 py-8 md:py-0"
      >
        <p
          class="text-white text-5xl font-black mb-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          85%
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-400 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] font-bold"
        >
          Victorias
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="group">
        <p
          class="text-secondary text-5xl font-black mb-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          Revés
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-400 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] font-bold"
        >
          Posición
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="perfil"
    class="py-32 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center"
  >
    <div class="relative">
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-secondary/30 translate-x-8 translate-y-8"
      >
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden relative z-10">
        <img
          src="../../src/assets/main-reves.webp"
          alt="Fondo decorativo Beto Montoya"
          class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 ease-in-out scale-105 hover:scale-100"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <h3 class="text-primary text-5xl font-black leading-tight">
        LA MENTALIDAD <br />
        <span class="text-secondary italic">DETRÁS DEL CRISTAL.</span>
      </h3>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-xl font-light">
        <p>
          Nacido para competir, he dedicado mi carrera a perfeccionar cada
          bandeja, cada salida de pared y cada remate por tres.
        </p>
        <p class="border-l-4 border-secondary pl-6 italic">
          "Mi enfoque no es solo la potencia, sino la lectura del juego. En el
          pádel profesional, la mente es tan importante como el brazo."
        </p>
      </div>

      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="inline-block mt-6 bg-primary text-white px-10 py-5 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-secondary hover:text-primary transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl"
      >
        Ver Biografía Completa
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-t border-gray-200">
    <p
      class="text-center text-gray-400 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] mb-12 font-bold"
    >
      Official Sponsors & Partners
    </p>
    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 md:gap-24 grayscale opacity-60 px-4"
    >
      <a
        href="https://www.hypesportsmx.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        class="transition-all hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100"
      >
        <span class="text-primary font-black text-3xl tracking-tighter italic"
          >HYPE<span class="text-secondary">STORE</span></span
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</GeneralLayout>
